name: Gabriel Sinclair
profile_summary: Our 29-year-old user is a Black African Descent man who identifies as straight and uses the pronouns He/Him/His. He is 6'1" tall and hails from Chicago, Illinois, but currently is in the dating scene in Los Angeles, California. He works in the Healthcare industry as a Physician and holds a Doctoral level education from the University of California, Berkeley. This Libra is an active individual who values honesty, family, health & fitness, and creativity. He is agnostic and politically moderate. As for hobbies, he enjoys traveling, photography, yoga, reading, and hiking. He speaks both English and Spanish and has a ENFJ personality type. He sometimes drinks, but does not smoke or use marijuana or drugs. Whilst not currently a parent, he is open to the idea of having children in the future. He also has a pet dog. His intention in dating is to find a life partner who shares monogamous beliefs.
